@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
    var updated = DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy");
}

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h1 class="mb-3">Privacy Notice</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: @updated</p>

        <p>
            This notice explains what personal data the AubgEMS website (“we”, “us”) collects,
            how we use it, and the choices you have. It applies to this site and the services
            available through it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="data-we-collect">1) Data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account data:</strong> email/username, password (hashed), and roles (Student/Organizer/Admin).</li>
            <li><strong>Profile & activity:</strong> events you create or join, timestamps, basic form inputs.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical:</strong> standard logs (IP address, user agent, request time) for security and debugging.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> essential auth/anti-forgery/session cookies required for the site to work.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="how-we-use">2) How we use your data</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide core features (sign in, join/leave events, “My Events”).</li>
            <li>Operate, secure, and improve the website.</li>
            <li>Administer organizer/admin functions (e.g., managing events, news, clubs).</li>
            <li>Respond to support requests or important service notices.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="legal-bases">3) Legal bases (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>
            Where applicable, we process data under: <em>contract necessity</em> (to deliver the site’s features),
            <em>legitimate interests</em> (security, service improvement), and <em>consent</em> when you knowingly submit
            optional information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="sharing">4) Sharing</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>With site administrators and authorized organizers to run events and manage content.</li>
            <li>With service providers (e.g., hosting/database) strictly to operate the site.</li>
            <li>When required by law or to protect the safety and security of the service.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-0"><strong>We do not sell your personal data.</strong></p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="retention">5) Retention</h2>
        <p>
            We keep your account and related event data while your account is active.
            If you delete your account (or request deletion), we remove or anonymize personal data
            within a reasonable period, subject to legal or operational requirements (e.g., audit logs).
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="your-rights">6) Your rights</h2>
        <p>
            You may have the right to access, correct, delete, restrict, or object to processing of your data,
            and to data portability. To exercise these rights, contact us using the information below.
            You can also lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="cookies">7) Cookies we use</h2>
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-sm table-bordered align-middle">
                <thead class="table-light">
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%">Cookie</th>
                    <th style="width: 25%">Type</th>
                    <th>Purpose</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>.AspNetCore.Identity.Application</td>
                    <td>Essential</td>
                    <td>Keeps you signed in (authentication cookie).</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>.AspNetCore.Antiforgery.*</td>
                    <td>Essential</td>
                    <td>Protects forms from CSRF attacks (anti-forgery token).</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>.AspNetCore.Session (if enabled)</td>
                    <td>Essential</td>
                    <td>Stores temporary session data to support site features.</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-0">
            We do <strong>not</strong> use advertising cookies. If analytics are introduced later, we will update this notice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="children">8) Students & minors</h2>
        <p>
            This site is intended for university use. If you are under the applicable age of consent for your
            region, please use the site only with appropriate permission or supervision as required by your
            institution’s policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="security">9) Security</h2>
        <p>
            We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data. No method of
            transmission or storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="changes">10) Changes to this notice</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this notice to reflect changes to the site or legal requirements. We will revise
            the “Last updated” date above and, where appropriate, provide additional notice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h5 mt-4" id="contact">11) Contact</h2>
        <p class="mb-0">
            Questions or privacy requests? Email <a href="mailto:ndp221@aubg.edu">ndp221@aubg.edu</a>
        </p>

        <div class="alert alert-warning mt-4 small mb-0">
            <strong>Note:</strong> This page is an informational template and not legal advice.
            Please adapt it to your institution’s policies and applicable laws.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">Summary</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ul class="list-unstyled small mb-0">
                    <li>✔ Essential cookies only</li>
                    <li>✔ No data sales</li>
                    <li>✔ Account & event data for service delivery</li>
                    <li>✔ You can request access/deletion</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>